[package]
name = "cryoglyph"
description = "Fast, simple 2D text rendering for wgpu"
version = "0.1.0"
edition = "2024"
repository = "https://github.com/iced-rs/cryoglyph"
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0 OR Zlib"

[dependencies]
etagere = "0.2"
cosmic-text = "0.14"
rustc-hash = "2"

[dependencies.wgpu]
version = "26"
default-features = false
features = ["wgsl"]

[dependencies.lru]
version = "0.16"
default-features = false

[dev-dependencies]
winit = "0.30"
pollster = "0.4"

[dev-dependencies.criterion]
version = "0.5"
features = ["html_reports"]

[[bench]]
name = "prepare"
harness = false

[package]
name = "dpi"
version = "0.1.1"
description = "Types for handling UI scaling"
keywords = ["DPI", "HiDPI", "scale-factor"]
categories = ["gui"]
rust-version = "1.70.0"
repository = "https://github.com/rust-windowing/winit"
license = "Apache-2.0"
edition = "2021"

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
features = ["serde", "mint"]
targets = ["i686-pc-windows-msvc", "x86_64-pc-windows-msvc", "x86_64-apple-darwin", "i686-unknown-linux-gnu", "x86_64-unknown-linux-gnu", "x86_64-apple-ios", "aarch64-linux-android", "wasm32-unknown-unknown"]
rustdoc-args = ["--cfg", "docsrs"]

[features]
serde = ["dep:serde"]
mint = ["dep:mint"]

[dependencies.serde]
optional = true
version = "1"
features = ["serde_derive"]

[dependencies.mint]
optional = true
version = "0.5.6"

[package]
name = "iced"
description = "A cross-platform GUI library inspired by Elm"
version = "0.14.0-dev"
edition = "2024"
authors = ["Héctor Ramón Jiménez <hector@hecrj.dev>"]
license = "MIT"
repository = "https://github.com/iced-rs/iced"
homepage = "https://iced.rs"
categories = ["gui"]
keywords = ["gui", "ui", "graphics", "interface", "widgets"]
rust-version = "1.88"

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
rustdoc-args = ["--cfg", "docsrs"]
all-features = true

[lints.rust]
missing_debug_implementations = "deny"
missing_docs = "deny"
unsafe_code = "deny"
unused_results = "deny"

[lints.rust.rust_2018_idioms]
level = "deny"
priority = -1

[lints.clippy]
type-complexity = "allow"
map-entry = "allow"
large-enum-variant = "allow"
result_large_err = "allow"
semicolon_if_nothing_returned = "deny"
trivially-copy-pass-by-ref = "deny"
default_trait_access = "deny"
match-wildcard-for-single-variants = "deny"
redundant-closure-for-method-calls = "deny"
filter_map_next = "deny"
manual_let_else = "deny"
unused_async = "deny"
from_over_into = "deny"
needless_borrow = "deny"
new_without_default = "deny"
useless_conversion = "deny"

[lints.rustdoc]
broken_intra_doc_links = "forbid"

[badges.maintenance]
status = "actively-developed"

[features]
default = ["wgpu", "tiny-skia", "crisp", "web-colors", "thread-pool", "linux-theme-detection"]
wgpu = ["iced_renderer/wgpu", "iced_widget/wgpu"]
tiny-skia = ["iced_renderer/tiny-skia"]
image = ["image-without-codecs", "image/default"]
image-without-codecs = ["iced_widget/image", "dep:image"]
svg = ["iced_widget/svg"]
canvas = ["iced_widget/canvas"]
qr_code = ["iced_widget/qr_code"]
markdown = ["iced_widget/markdown"]
lazy = ["iced_widget/lazy"]
debug = ["iced_winit/debug", "iced_devtools"]
time-travel = ["debug", "iced_devtools/time-travel"]
hot = ["debug", "iced_debug/hot"]
thread-pool = ["iced_futures/thread-pool"]
tokio = ["iced_futures/tokio"]
smol = ["iced_futures/smol"]
sysinfo = ["iced_winit/sysinfo"]
web-colors = ["iced_renderer/web-colors"]
crisp = ["iced_core/crisp", "iced_widget/crisp"]
webgl = ["iced_renderer/webgl"]
highlighter = ["iced_highlighter", "iced_widget/highlighter"]
advanced = ["iced_core/advanced", "iced_widget/advanced"]
fira-sans = ["iced_renderer/fira-sans"]
basic-shaping = ["iced_core/basic-shaping"]
advanced-shaping = ["iced_core/advanced-shaping"]
strict-assertions = ["iced_renderer/strict-assertions"]
unconditional-rendering = ["iced_winit/unconditional-rendering"]
sipper = ["iced_runtime/sipper"]
linux-theme-detection = ["iced_winit/linux-theme-detection"]

[dependencies]
thiserror = "1.0"

[dependencies.iced_debug]
version = "0.14.0-dev"
path = "debug"

[dependencies.iced_core]
version = "0.14.0-dev"
path = "core"

[dependencies.iced_futures]
version = "0.14.0-dev"
path = "futures"

[dependencies.iced_renderer]
version = "0.14.0-dev"
path = "renderer"

[dependencies.iced_runtime]
version = "0.14.0-dev"
path = "runtime"

[dependencies.iced_widget]
version = "0.14.0-dev"
path = "widget"

[dependencies.iced_winit]
features = ["program"]
version = "0.14.0-dev"
path = "winit"

[dependencies.iced_devtools]
optional = true
version = "0.14.0-dev"
path = "devtools"

[dependencies.iced_highlighter]
optional = true
version = "0.14.0-dev"
path = "highlighter"

[dependencies.image]
optional = true
version = "0.25"
default-features = false

[dev-dependencies]
criterion = "0.5"

[dev-dependencies.iced_wgpu]
version = "0.14.0-dev"
path = "wgpu"

[[bench]]
name = "wgpu"
harness = false
required-features = ["canvas"]

[profile.release-opt]
inherits = "release"
codegen-units = 1
debug = false
lto = true
incremental = false
opt-level = 3
overflow-checks = false
strip = "debuginfo"

[workspace]
members = ["beacon", "core", "debug", "devtools", "futures", "graphics", "highlighter", "program", "renderer", "runtime", "test", "tiny_skia", "wgpu", "widget", "winit", "examples/*"]

js-sys = "0.3.70"
pin-project = "1"
wasm-bindgen = "0.2.93"
wasm-bindgen-futures = "0.4.43"
web-time = "1"

[target."cfg(target_family = \"wasm\")".dependencies.web_sys]
package = "web-sys"
version = "0.3.70"
features = ["AbortController", "AbortSignal", "Blob", "BlobPropertyBag", "console", "CssStyleDeclaration", "Document", "DomException", "DomRect", "DomRectReadOnly", "Element", "Event", "EventTarget", "FocusEvent", "HtmlCanvasElement", "HtmlElement", "HtmlImageElement", "ImageBitmap", "ImageBitmapOptions", "ImageBitmapRenderingContext", "ImageData", "IntersectionObserver", "IntersectionObserverEntry", "KeyboardEvent", "MediaQueryList", "MessageChannel", "MessagePort", "Navigator", "Node", "OrientationLockType", "OrientationType", "PageTransitionEvent", "Permissions", "PermissionState", "PermissionStatus", "PointerEvent", "PremultiplyAlpha", "ResizeObserver", "ResizeObserverBoxOptions", "ResizeObserverEntry", "ResizeObserverOptions", "ResizeObserverSize", "Screen", "ScreenOrientation", "Url", "VisibilityState", "WheelEvent", "Window", "Worker"]

[target."cfg(target_family = \"wasm\")".dev-dependencies]
console_error_panic_hook = "0.1"
tracing-web = "0.1"

[target."cfg(all(target_family = \"wasm\", target_feature = \"atomics\"))".dependencies]
atomic-waker = "1"

[target."cfg(all(target_family = \"wasm\", target_feature = \"atomics\"))".dependencies.concurrent-queue]
version = "2"
default-features = false

[[example]]
doc-scrape-examples = true
name = "window"

[workspace]
resolver = "2"
members = ["dpi"]

[workspace.package]
rust-version = "1.70.0"
repository = "https://github.com/rust-windowing/winit"
license = "Apache-2.0"
edition = "2021"

[workspace.dependencies]
mint = "0.5.6"

[workspace.dependencies.serde]
version = "1"
features = ["serde_derive"]

[source.vendored-sources]
directory = "cargo/vendor"

[source.crates-io]
replace-with = "vendored-sources"

[source."https://github.com/iced-rs/cryoglyph"]
git = "https://github.com/iced-rs/cryoglyph"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
rev = "453cedec0d2ec563bd7fa87e84a2319bcebb1ba3"

[source."https://github.com/iced-rs/winit"]
git = "https://github.com/iced-rs/winit"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
rev = "11414b6aa45699f038114e61b4ddf5102b2d3b4b"

[source."https://github.com/iced-rs/iced"]
git = "https://github.com/iced-rs/iced"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
